This paper is primarily focused on object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of game theory to optimize data augmentation is a machine learning approach, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of perturbations and optimization, which are topics in data science (cs.DS) and neural networks (cs.NE).
